# Pho 99 Grill — Project Overview

Marketing landing page for **Pho 99 Grill**, a Vietnamese pho + grill restaurant.

## Stack

- Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19 + TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4 (CSS-first config via `@theme inline` in `app/globals.css`)
- ESLint (`eslint-config-next`)
- `next/font` for Google Fonts; `next/image` for images
- Turbopack dev/build

## Brand

- Name: **Pho 99 Grill** (display the wordmark as `phở 99` lowercase, accent on "phở")
- Tone: warm, family-run, ingredient-driven; "slow-simmered phở and flame-grilled Vietnamese classics"
- Copy is placeholder until the owner provides the real menu/hours/location — keep it editable in one obvious spot per section.

## Design references (do NOT ship)

- `Inspo/` contains saved HTML of two reference sites for visual inspiration only. It is in `.gitignore` and must never be imported, copied verbatim, or referenced from runtime code.
  - Cafe Avalaun → reference for **landing page section structure** (stacked full-bleed scroll sections).
  - Uchi → reference for the **header / nav** (fixed, scroll-aware, lowercase, slide-out drawer) and the warm beige palette.

## Layout conventions

- Components live in `app/_components/` (underscore prefix keeps them out of the route tree).
- Section components live in `app/_components/sections/`.
- Hooks live in `app/_lib/`.
- Path alias `@/*` maps to the project root.
